title: Training Cup - Dr. Brown's Soft Spout Transition Cup
description:
Dr. Brown's Soft Spout Transition Cup
The best way to help baby make the easy transition from bottle to cup. This “first cup” is now even better with sturdy, contoured handles that make it easier than ever for little hands to get a comfortable grip. Features a one-piece, spill-proof silicone spout valve that makes sipping easy for tiny mouths, and is also removable for easy cleaning. Attached lid stays open when baby drinks and keeps spout clean when not in use. 

• Easy to assemble and clean
• Dishwasher safe
• 6 oz/180 ml
• Recommended for babies 6 months +
• Choose from a selection of vibrant colors
